Name: Steem Pending Payout Checker
Contributors: @akintunde @odl {steemit.com usernames}
Programmed with: PHP
Requires at least: php 5.6 
Major Dependencies: Steemjs API
License: APACHE LICENSE
License URI: https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0
APP Address: check.akin.com.ng

Short Summary:
This script calculates the pending payout of steem blockchain users.It can tested in the app address.

Description:
This script help to solve the ambiguity associated with knowing the expected payout of a user at any 7 day period which is the interval of payment for every comment or post made on steemit.com, utopian-io, busy.org, zappl and the rest of the apps that use the steem blockchain.

I you don't know about the steem blockchain , you can read about it here.

This script was forke from another script by @odl. 

How to it works:
1) The Script has an index page that has a form as shown below:

Users will have to fill this form with their username, submit and then they will be directed to the action page (result.php) where the script will link the steemjs api to bring in all their posts details including resteemed posts, then generate a table containging all details while their sbd payouts gets added up as shown below;

The script also  has an htaccess file that processes the fancy url to allow users use an address like this (check.akin.com.ng/@akintunde) or (check.akin.com.ng/akintunde). This depends on the domain name that this script uses.

